        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "That's your preference. Many clients provide a door code or spare key and aren't home during cleanings. Trustworthy companies conduct background checks on all staff. If you prefer to be present for your first cleaning, that's completely reasonable."
      }
    }
  ]
