        </p>

        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Hiring locally also means faster response times and accountability within your own community. When something goes wrong (and eventually, something always does), you want a company that will make it right because their reputation depends on it.
        </p>

        <!-- COMPARISON SECTION - Strategic Positioning -->
