          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Standard cleaning, deep cleaning, move-in/move-out cleaning, recurring maintenance plans (weekly, bi-weekly, monthly), Airbnb turnover cleaning, and commercial cleaning.
          </p>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium mb-4">What Sets Them Apart:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2 text-lg text-gray-600">
            <li>Transparent pricing starting at $125 (no hidden fees or surprise charges)</li>
            <li>Background-checked, professionally trained cleaning specialists</li>
            <li>100% satisfaction guarantee on every cleaning</li>
            <li>$2M liability insurance coverage</li>
