        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Get Your Free Quote Today</p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">Response within 2 hours. Service throughout the Shoals area.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="tel:2568261100" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition">
